<BaseLayout title="About - National Park Directory">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center my-16">About Us</h1>
		
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
			<p>Welcome to the National Park Directory, your comprehensive guide to exploring the natural wonders of America's national parks.</p>
			
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>Our mission is to connect people with the beauty and wonder of national parks across the country. We believe that everyone should have access to accurate, up-to-date information about these natural treasures.</p>
			
			<h2>What We Offer</h2>
			<p>The National Park Directory provides detailed information about parks, including:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Comprehensive guides to each national park</li>
				<li>Visitor information and tips</li>
				<li>Hiking and trail guides</li>
				<li>Wildlife spotting guides</li>
				<li>Seasonal highlights and recommendations</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h2>Our Team</h2>
			<p>Our team consists of outdoor enthusiasts, photographers, and conservation advocates who are passionate about national parks. We've visited many of the parks we feature and work diligently to provide accurate, helpful information to our users.</p>
			
			<h2>Join Our Community</h2>
			<p>We invite you to join our community of park enthusiasts. Share your experiences, photos, and tips with fellow nature lovers. Together, we can help preserve these natural wonders for generations to come.</p>
			
			<p>Thank you for visiting the National Park Directory. We hope our resources help you plan your next adventure in the great outdoors!</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout> 